<div class="container" id="all-about">
  <div class="row justify-content-md-center">
    <div class="col-8 mt-4">
      <div class="card text-center shadow mb-5 bg-white rounded">
        <div class="card-header">
          About this blog      
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5 class="card-title" id="article-link">Objective</h5>
          <p class="card-text"style="text-align: left">This blog features CRUD functions, multiple resources, an authentication system built from scratch, a front-end using Bootstrap 5, has one-to-many and many-to-many associations at DB layer, and was built using Rails 6. This is my first fullstack app utilizing a Rails front and back end!
          </p>
          <br>
          <p class="card-text" style="text-align: center">
          Happy you're here.  
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-footer text-muted" id="footer-link">
          <%= link_to "View all articles", articles_path%>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
